OL,3,C'They were human beings': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers must be 'at the heart' of
OL,5,CManston probe
OL,7,FAn inquiry into the "overcrowded,
OL,8,Fsqualid and unsanitary" conditions for
OL,9,Fasylum seekers at Manston processing
OL,10,Fcentre in 2022 has been told to put
OL,11,Fthose detained there "at the heart" of
OL,12,Fthe probe.
OL,14,FThe non-statutory investigation held
OL,15,Fits first public meeting on Thursday
OL,16,Fafter it first launched on March 17
OL,17,Flast year.
