OL,3,C'They were human beings': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers must be 'at the heart' of
OL,5,CManston probe
OL,7,FThe investigation is looking at the
OL,8,F"decisions, actions and circumstances"
OL,9,Fwhich led to the conditions
OL,10,Fexperienced by people at Manston Short-
OL,11,FTerm Holding Facility in Kent between
OL,12,FJune and November 2022.
OL,14,FManston was at points "significantly
OL,15,Fovercapacity", stretching from its
OL,16,Fcapacity level of 1,650 people to
OL,17,F4,000 at the height of the pressures
OL,18,Fwhere conditions "deteriorated over
OL,19,Ftime", the inquiry heard.
