OL,3,C'They were human beings': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers must be 'at the heart' of
OL,5,CManston probe
OL,7,F"They should, we suggest, be at the
OL,8,Fheart of this inquiry."
OL,10,FThe inquiry heard the probe will
OL,11,Fconsider evidence of misconduct by
OL,12,Fsome staff members, alongside human
OL,13,Fexperiences, legal compliance and
OL,14,Finfectious diseases.
OL,16,F"The fact that a detainee died during
OL,17,Fthe period of his detention from
OL,18,Fdiphtheria brings this issue into
OL,19,Fsharp focus," lead counsel to the
OL,20,Finquiry Clair Dobbin KC said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
