OL,3,C'They were human beings': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers must be 'at the heart' of
OL,5,CManston probe
OL,7,FHussein Haseeb Ahmed, 31, died at the
OL,8,FQueen Elizabeth the Queen Mother
OL,9,FHospital in Margate on November 19
OL,10,Fafter being held at Manston after
OL,11,Fcrossing the Channel a week earlier.
OL,13,FThe inquiry's scope has been expanded
OL,14,Fto include addressing how he died and
OL,15,Fthe circumstances of his death.
OL,17,FMs Dobbin said: "In this inquiry,
OL,18,Fstark issues arise because people were
OL,19,Fbeing detained in large numbers in
OL,20,Fconditions which were not intended for
OL,21,Fdetention beyond 24 hours.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
