OL,3,C'They were human beings': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers must be 'at the heart' of
OL,5,CManston probe
OL,7,F"The net result was not simply people
OL,8,Fremained at Manston beyond 24 hours
OL,9,Fbut they were in conditions not
OL,10,Fdesigned for staying in any sort of
OL,11,Flong term, and which at points became
OL,12,Fovercrowded, squalid and unsanitary."
OL,14,FShe also set out that the inquiry's
OL,15,Fapproach is for fair process and
OL,16,Fdignity for all participants.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
