OL,3,C'They were human beings': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers must be 'at the heart' of
OL,5,CManston probe
OL,7,FMs Dobbin said: "The arrival of people
OL,8,Fon small boats is a divisive and
OL,9,Femotive issue in the United Kingdom,
OL,10,Fbut this inquiry is not a commission
OL,11,Finto migration or the seeking of
OL,12,Fasylum, and nor has it been set up to
OL,13,Fconsider the reasons why specific
OL,14,Findividuals have come to enter the UK
OL,15,Fby boat.
OL,17,F"Its principal concern is the
OL,18,Fconditions in which those men, women
OL,19,Fand children were kept upon their
OL,20,Farrival at Manston and why those
OL,21,Fconditions arose."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
